Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.25,0:01:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pumpkin Pirates, charge!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The treasure we're after is on that island!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.56,0:02:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever makes land first gets a reward!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.19,0:02:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me! I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.86,0:02:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.87,0:02:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you're a grown-up, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.88,0:02:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.71,0:02:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rapa Nui! Isoka! Rongo! Akibi! Pukau!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me here! \NDon't leave me all by myself!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.69,0:02:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I was dreaming...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're concerned about your friends, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You were calling out their names in your sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.11,0:03:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it all for, exactly?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.32,0:03:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,These last 50 years that I dedicated \Nto researching the Rainbow Mist?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.33,0:03:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing Rapa Nui and the others \Nthe way they were back then,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.71,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes me think that I, at least, \Nhave wasted all that time.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.42,0:03:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't wasted, right? \NYou did get to see all your old friends again.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.89,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the ship moving?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't be...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Forward!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.20,0:03:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy, are you sure we're moving forward?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.53,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Straight ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where on earth are you headed?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? We're going out of the mist!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.21,0:03:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you wander into Ape's Concert, \Nyou never get out of it again.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fiendish region of the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.51,0:04:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't we see that ship a little while ago?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There are ships that look \Nalike everywhere you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.64,0:04:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this ship ran aground in the \Nvery first place we dropped anchor.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.10,0:04:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember seeing the goddess on the bow.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.57,0:04:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Does that mean we've come \Nback to where we started from?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.86,0:04:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I asked if you \Nwere sure we're going forward!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching! \NWe've been going straight.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.82,0:04:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't see our way \Nstraight in this mist, can you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.02,0:04:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Seis Fleurs!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what was that for?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.02,0:04:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We shot forward, but it came \Nflying in from behind us!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.31,0:04:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.86,0:05:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Space is being distorted.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.36,0:05:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered something written in the book.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.66,0:05:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The inside of the Rainbow Mist is like a maze.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, don't do anything crazy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.83,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...Rocket!!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.50,0:05:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.83,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't necessarily return to the same location.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.01,0:05:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. This is a strange mist, \Nwhere no matter how far you go,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you end up where you started.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a "strange mist."
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.37,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The part about not being able \Nto get out of here, at least.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to get out. It's fun in here!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.91,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we do!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.12,0:05:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's join up with Rapa Nui and the others.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.79,0:05:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,With those kids?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.01,0:05:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The best way to get ourselves \Nout of Ape's Concert
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.37,0:06:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is to consult the ones whose territory it is, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.71,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but where are they?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask that boy over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.26,0:06:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How did she find me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.64,0:06:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use hiding.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Un Fleur.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you take us?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.86,0:06:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To wherever your boss is?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.53,0:06:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.66,0:06:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Henzo came back, \Nand he's an old man, you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of joke is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no joke.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.96,0:06:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He fell into the sea, in order to save us, \Nand we haven't seen him since.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise, I'll come after you later!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.63,0:06:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on! Keep going! Don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still alive, in the outside world.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.18,0:06:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Henzo said that he's been \Nlooking for a way to bring us back,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.68,0:07:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,all this time, in Luluka, and that \N50 years had passed, just like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.48,0:07:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,50 years? That's absurd.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.35,0:07:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that old man \Nisn't playing a trick on you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he play a trick on us?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know why.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.41,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But if what Henzo said is true,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.45,0:07:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's happened to the town of Luluka.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad... Mom...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.50,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no use in worrying about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll know if it's true or not once \Nyou go back and see for yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know of a way to get back?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.84,0:07:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do. I'm the raiding captain \Nof the Wetton Pirates, Ian-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.31,0:07:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us the way to get back \Nto the town of Luluka!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.35,0:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! Just bring the key! \NIf you let me out of here,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.36,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'll take charge of you, \Nand return you to your homes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.70,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rongo! Akibi!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him fool you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian just wants to get out of there.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.16,0:08:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying that he knows a way to \Nthe outside world is just a ruse.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A ruse?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.38,0:08:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are a tough one, Isoka-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.13,0:08:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't forgotten all those \Ntimes you mistreated us.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.85,0:08:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, you tenderfoots!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.22,0:08:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Being on the seas means always \Nbeing side by side with danger!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.74,0:08:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to survive, then follow the orders
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.65,0:08:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Wetton Pirates' raiding captain, Ian-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.36,0:08:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing! \NThat ship over there is full of jewels, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.66,0:08:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, take it to the captain's quarters.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.84,0:08:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They also had all this food!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, take that to the captain's quarters, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea serpent!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.01,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away, face it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Rongo!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Rapa Nui!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.61,0:09:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at me like that for?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.08,0:09:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at your gloomy faces \Nis making the food taste bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.25,0:09:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, it's only because \NI happened to be aboard this ship
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.02,0:09:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that you've managed to stay alive up to now!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You might at least say thank you,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.93,0:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't recall {\i1}ever{\i0} getting \Nlooks as critical as this!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.27,0:09:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He was drawn here by the \Nsmell of the food, was he?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.82,0:09:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, get outside!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.41,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, wait! This is my ship! Defend the ship!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your boat is more important than everyone's lives?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.96,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need a leader like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.14,0:10:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! My ship...!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.23,0:10:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're better off without that ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Our true departure is just getting started.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.61,0:10:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all fed up with you, \Nalways shooting your mouth off,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and only thinking about yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.61,0:10:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you must hate me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.41,0:10:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if I really {\i1}do{\i0} know a way out of here?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Another transparent lie!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and test me, to see if I'm lying.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.76,0:11:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're concerned about the town \Nof Luluka, too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.26,0:11:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we get all of the dormant \Ntreasures of Ape's Concert together,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.01,0:11:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we can live without doing \Nanything until the day we die!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.35,0:11:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to live as pirates \Nhere in this hazy mist.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.35,0:11:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? \NCome with me, back to the outside world.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.02,0:11:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Our only leader is Rapa Nui. \NNone of us are going to follow you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.33,0:11:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, there's no making headway with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.03,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, take your time and \Nthink it over, Isoka-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.18,0:11:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a ship coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.83,0:11:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, prepare for combat! \NFortify our defenses!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.09,0:11:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How did they know where we are?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.89,0:11:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pukau!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.73,0:11:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That ship is huge!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.56,0:11:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a wrecked warship, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.98,0:11:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Right now, though, it's our hideout.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.07,0:12:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You cowards!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you hold Pukau?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No more talk!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Release Pukau!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayor! It's the Talielisin!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.98,0:12:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my dear old ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.73,0:12:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But Grandpa, why is this ship \Ncoming back home now?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.24,0:12:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yow!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to call me "Mayor"!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.91,0:12:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.70,0:12:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Look there.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.62,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,50 years ago, my ship \Ndisappeared inside that mist.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And, since the ship has returned,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.25,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it means that the doorway to \NApe's Concert has been opened.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's now or never,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.55,0:13:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,if we want to get the treasure inside there, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.09,0:13:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. But how do you know that?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.89,0:13:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your grandson there told me so.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.56,0:13:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You bonehead!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.22,0:13:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And after everything I said \Nabout the treasure being a secret!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.23,0:13:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Grandp... I mean, Mayor.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.06,0:13:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure must be trouble, \Nhaving dimwitted family members, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.61,0:13:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't that the truth? And why are \Nyou acting sympathetic toward me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.53,0:13:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For whatever reasons, now that you \Nknow the secret of Ape's Concert,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford you leaving.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to silence us, is that it?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.87,0:13:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're going to pay the \N"I found out the secret" tax
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.29,0:13:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of ten million Berries.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.30,0:13:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a joke?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,More to the point, that's too much!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.80,0:13:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,More to the point, what kind of tax is that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.57,0:13:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you can't pay the tax?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.05,0:13:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tax collection squad!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You called, Mayor Wetton?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.98,0:14:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Daddy!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.49,0:14:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them to Rainbow Tower, \Nand condemn them to hard labor.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.71,0:14:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That is Rainbow Tower.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.87,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You are going to keep working \Nat that tower until you die.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.71,0:14:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hellish, heavy labor, from morning until night.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.55,0:14:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be off to the next world in no time.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.55,0:14:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, Flip, take them away.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.26,0:14:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Rainbow Mist has appeared, hasn't it, Father?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.35,0:14:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is our chance to get the \Ntreasure from Ape's Concert!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He just said everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.43,0:14:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Secrets aren't worth a damn to them, are they?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.69,0:14:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All three generations are patently stupid.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.11,0:14:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You bonehead! Fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.90,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Call in Henzo, and have him \Ninvestigate the Rainbow Mist!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.91,0:14:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Bring me the transponder snail, at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.91,0:14:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Father, you're still pretty strong, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.24,0:14:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, calm down a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.58,0:15:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You took Pukau hostage,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.21,0:15:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and forced him to tell you \Nwhere our base is, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be disgraceful.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Rapa Nui, I'm not a hostage!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.51,0:15:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They just asked me to lead \Nthem here, so I brought them!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They threatened you, to make you say that!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.39,0:15:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth! \NThese people aren't bad, I tell you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.66,0:15:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, he doesn't get mad, even when I do this!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.03,0:15:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not true! This is all a strategy, \Nto get us to let our guards down!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You misunderstand.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.32,0:15:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want to know how \Nto get out of Ape's Concert.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you find out?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're planning to take all the \Ntreasures out of these shipwrecks,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and run off with them!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.42,0:15:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me, Rapa Nui, these guys, \Nat least, wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.80,0:15:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I believe the words of a grown-up?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.41,0:15:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of {\i1}course{\i0} they're out to get the treasure!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going nowhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.55,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.18,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Usopp's specially made lunch is ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.56,0:16:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo! Food!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.85,0:16:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys want some, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.65,0:16:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't vouch for the taste, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who asked you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum! Did you really make this?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.99,0:16:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can't do. Hey, Luffy! \NDon't eat those all yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.32,0:16:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not as good as Sanji's, \Nbut they are just regular yummy.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.87,0:16:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks. I lived alone for a long time and all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There are some children over there \Nwho look like they'd like some.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on down, guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.88,0:16:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,These are delicious!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.46,0:16:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, can we really?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.84,0:16:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.93,0:16:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them sucker you in with food!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.55,0:16:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten your \Npride as Pumpkin Pirates?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rapa Nui!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.89,0:16:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Pride won't fill your belly.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.06,0:16:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You guys came from the East Blue?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.03,0:16:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means, you must have \Ngone past Reverse Mountain, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.36,0:16:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got guts!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.36,0:17:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we've gone through \Nmany adventures up to now.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.49,0:17:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We've dueled with Giants, and sea \Nserpents that swallow whole islands,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.50,0:17:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and even saved a country from a secret society.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.29,0:17:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.96,0:17:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.67,0:17:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason we got \Nthrough those predicaments
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.51,0:17:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is because we had my wisdom and bravery!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.98,0:17:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of reverence for that, \Neveryone calls me "Captain..."
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop sputtering when others are eating.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Rapa Nui, forgive me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.25,0:17:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive my shameful self! \NI spent 50 years researching a way
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.33,0:17:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to save you from the Rainbow Mist,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.12,0:17:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally managed to get myself inside the mist,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.33,0:17:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but thanks to my carelessness, we can't get out.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a failure as a pirate professor!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will endure my shame to ask you,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.88,0:18:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,if you know a way, please tell me! \NHow do we get out of this mist?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.85,0:18:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, we can leave here, \Ntogether, and go back to our home.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way out.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.44,0:18:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if I did know of one, \NI wouldn't tell you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.90,0:18:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't trust you guys, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.41,0:18:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And you call yourselves friends?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.24,0:18:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind us, Pops here is your friend, isn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.20,0:18:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, if you can't trust your friends, \Nwho can you trust?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.83,0:18:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep out of this!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.00,0:18:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You expect me to just believe that \N50 years have suddenly gone by?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.02,0:18:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.26,0:18:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much time has passed, \Nor how different he looks,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.22,0:18:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,if he's one of your friends, who fell \Nin under the same banner as you,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you should know each other!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.56,0:18:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The color of your flag may fade, \Nbut friendship is forever, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.78,0:18:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.28,0:19:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, I'm coming. Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What good does it do for you to answer?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.49,0:19:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, Professor Henzo?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.63,0:19:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.83,0:19:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, is that you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.42,0:19:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.42,0:19:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys just took the ship on your own,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.17,0:19:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and put the rest of us in a big fix!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that you, Nami?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.65,0:19:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're connected to Nami and the others?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.85,0:19:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,– Nami? \N– Hold on, if we can talk to her...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.44,0:19:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we connecting to the outside world?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Flip?! Flip, are you there?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.52,0:19:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Flip!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Henzo, where are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.86,0:19:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm inside the Rainbow Mist.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.24,0:19:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rainbow...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...Mist?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.90,0:19:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, we are unable to get out.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.87,0:19:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but could you come rescue us?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.09,0:19:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's coming for us?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.67,0:19:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go back to Luluka, right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Rapa Nui?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.38,0:20:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time. \NTell Wetton to equip the safety search gear
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.09,0:20:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that I invented, and to come inside the mist.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Also—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.31,0:20:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That name you just said, Wetton,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.06,0:20:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is the same man who burned \Ndown the town of Luluka, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.36,0:20:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I had to team up with that man, \Nin order to save all of you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.25,0:20:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's all clear. \NYou are not the Henzo that we know!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.91,0:20:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were one of the Pumpkin Pirates,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.71,0:20:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no way you'd become one of Wetton's pawns!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.36,0:20:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rapa Nui...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me by that name!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You traitor!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.50,0:20:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.84,0:20:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, so they really {\i1}are{\i0} \Ninside that mist, are they?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.25,0:20:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.26,0:20:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? We go inside the mist.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.60,0:20:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you aren't allowed to go into \NApe's Concert without my permission.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.77,0:21:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep acting on your own, and...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.49,0:21:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, where is that safety gear \Nthat he mentioned earlier?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.86,0:21:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, in here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.07,0:21:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't mention it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you giving it to them for?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.33,0:21:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.91,0:21:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools! Seize them, at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.17,0:21:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.04,0:21:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And here, I was about to make \Na wisecrack about eloping.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.10,0:21:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Nami!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.93,0:21:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Leave Luffy and the others, \Nand the treasure, to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.73,0:21:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.95,0:21:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.41,0:23:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.45,0:23:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Nami.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.91,0:23:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "oh, it's you"?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.74,0:23:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And after I came all the way \Nhere just to rescue you!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.08,0:23:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.04,0:23:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.83,0:23:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's disappeared beyond the mist.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.34,0:23:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.50,0:23:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.55,0:23:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,An Inevitable Melee! \NWetton's Schemes and the Rainbow Tower
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.09,0:23:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
